Package: NDlib
Title: A list of handy functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Li Yim", email = "a.y.liyim@amc.uva.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains several functions which are relevant to the analysis of DNA methylation (obtained from Illumina HumanMethylation BeadChips or sequencing).
Depends: GenomicRanges, ggplot2, gridExtra, Gviz, R (>= 3.2.2)
